'''Google Inc.''' ([[NASDAQ]]: '''GOOG''') is a [[United States|U.S.]] based corporation, founded in [[1998]] that runs and manages the [[Google]] [[search engine]]. Google is headquartered (at the "[[Googleplex]]") in [[Mountain View, Santa Clara County, California|Mountain View]], [[California]] and employs over 1,000 workers. Google's [[CEO]] became [[Eric Schmidt|Dr. Eric Schmidt]] (he was previously the CEO of [[Novell]]) when co-founder [[Larry Page]] stepped down.
